img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 首先要去VA(邵逸夫樓)整返張臨時學生會會員證，同時要帶備返Notice of offer (取錄通知書) ，身份證，財務處繳費單Cap圖(Su fee)，繳費方法收據同埋現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 登記完會有返個袋同貼紙，入面有本「理攻」同「我講理知」，巴打你可以用嚟更加了解poly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 之後就可以去邵逸夫體育館搵SHTM Students' Association (SHTMSA) 嘅booth到報中O啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係佢地個Facebook Page同理工大學學生會個網都睇到 佢地個Ocamp會係8月25至27號搞! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個時我諗到無諗就報左Ocamp 一班人係到跳舞同玩Game真係幾熱血架 所以玩完之後真係無後悔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比條Link巴打你參考下啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/14Genial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F14Genial%2F&d=AjvRlTjlLkzCUhfqY%2B9740kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=4847c91c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/14Genial/</a>"},{"pid":"287dfb470f8e1d553e7f4575b68f880883261501","tid":771800,"uid":135821,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91daca4377b89407285c82afebdf37d04f68e94d","tid":771800,"uid":199015,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:59:00.000Z","msg":"恭喜巴打你入到Poly Hotel Man呀！如果你入到呢科你可以玩返個Faculty搞既Ocamp 可以識返自己科既朋友仔同埋師兄姐 到時上堂都唔洗咁悶同埋有得拎下Sources嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n只要Jupas入左JS3296都可以報SHTM (School of Hotel and Tourism Management 酒店及旅遊業管理學院)呢一個Faculty既Ocamp！<br />\n<br />\n上網搵左小小資料 佢地既Oday會係8月12至13日星期日同一10：00-18：00係邵逸夫體育館搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 首先要去VA(邵逸夫樓)整返張臨時學生會會員證，同時要帶備返Notice of offer (取錄通知書) ，身份證，財務處繳費單Cap圖(Su fee)，繳費方法收據同埋現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 登記完會有返個袋同貼紙，入面有本「理攻」同「我講理知」，巴打你可以用嚟更加了解poly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 之後就可以去邵逸夫體育館搵SHTM Students' Association (SHTMSA) 嘅booth到報中O啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係佢地個Facebook Page同理工大學學生會個網都睇到 佢地個Ocamp會係8月25至27號搞! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個時我諗到無諗就報左Ocamp 一班人係到跳舞同玩Game真係幾熱血架 所以玩完之後真係無後悔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n比條Link巴打你參考下啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/14Genial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F14Genial%2F&d=AjvRlTjlLkzCUhfqY%2B9740kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=4847c91c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/14Genial/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T10:00:29.000Z","msg":"麻煩曬巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada33af7dcf3a54ea48c4c6d7baeac159b905423","tid":771800,"uid":128112,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T10:08:07.000Z","msg":"我淨係想知係咪多女"},{"pid":"66855e7f695a45376b2b6c3513bfa8fa4bd11766","tid":771800,"uid":199018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2d94acd6eb40a5ba9375debf75879ceb2b6ad9a1","tid":771800,"uid":135821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"小弟今年入左PolyU Hotel Man<br />\n有無巴打絲打知道Ocamp點報同埋有乜推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講係咪好多女女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"巴打諗唔諗住一齊組團去報 第一次去呢啲function有啲緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as